def: Any one of several species of actinians belonging to the genusCerianthus. These animals have a long, smooth body tapering to thebase, and two separate circles of tentacles around the mouth. Theyform a tough, flexible, feltlike tube with a smooth internal lining,in which they dwell, whence the name.
The person to whom a warrant or warranty is made.
A small house or building at a little distance from the mainhouse; an outbuilding.
Composed of, or having, tufted or matted filaments like tow;stupeous.
A tie consisting of a series of connected iron bars or rods.
A West Indian duck, sometimes domesticated.
To speak or write with exaggeration. Bp. Montagu.
Producing one seed only in a seed pod.
